/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女人真係絕撚到仆街<br />\n冷血 無感覺"},{"pid":"c89c2b11b74c3f50db8fc29810839824ddbb9c55","tid":174444,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T22:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>連朋友都唔想做？<br />\n我仲好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因乜事分手先？</blockquote><br />\n我自己好衝動講咗分手 因為安全感問題<br />\n但依家諗返起都覺得自己好戇鳩 佢其實對我好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事後我有挽回 但佢話佢都諗清楚都係分手算<br />\n佢話有分手念頭就係已經破壞咗成段關係 唉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 低撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd45b47278872b82ac5bdc9cedc7996748e2bc19","tid":174444,"uid":72783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T22:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多時候，分左手先黎後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6a8b146ce94daa2f33481a4e4397c1052fa9b6","tid":174444,"uid":72783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T22:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>連朋友都唔想做？<br />\n我仲好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因乜事分手先？</blockquote><br />\n我自己好衝動講咗分手 因為安全感問題<br />\n但依家諗返起都覺得自己好戇鳩 佢其實對我好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事後我有挽回 但佢話佢都諗清楚都係分手算<br />\n佢話有分手念頭就係已經破壞咗成段關係 唉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 低撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2c212e2fbba76f16f02117f23d8c8a11383f51","tid":174444,"uid":71144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T22:40:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多時候，分左手先黎後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一係你就搵番人 一係你就搵第二個<br />\n後悔嚟都無用 <br />\n有心有誠意有堅持 就自然打動到 <br />\n男人表面堅定 實際個心好軟<br />\n但係唔好俾架子 溫柔少少 <br />\n試左衰左唔得就算"},{"pid":"0b71970067d6c5ac72d2e4b1f70642d273fbb9bc","tid":174444,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T22:56:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>女人先絕呀</blockquote><br />\n岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女人真係絕撚到仆街<br />\n冷血 無感覺</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe7864a71e3b957980dbfa239ab1284fc4b41f5","tid":174444,"uid":28838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T22:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>女人先絕呀</blockquote><br />\n岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女人真係絕撚到仆街<br />\n冷血 無感覺</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAfter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9b47746b1865e7b09812a61d654ecc2cb3a690","tid":174444,"uid":28838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T22:58:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>女人先絕呀</blockquote><br />\n岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女人真係絕撚到仆街<br />\n冷血 無感覺</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAfter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8bce86c720bb566b4406fa3403c9323e903dc2","tid":174444,"uid":44085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T23:04:30.000Z","msg":"樓主你男朋友分分鐘出面有件<br />\n咁岩你又開口講分手仲唔順勢咩<br />\n真係鐘意你點會咁絕，男人係咁賤<br />\n利申：賤人"},{"pid":"9482c3342dc45aceab83e3763334cc39cfc03d0d","tid":174444,"uid":96515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T23:04:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>連朋友都唔想做？<br />\n我仲好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因乜事分手先？</blockquote><br />\n我自己好衝動講咗分手 因為安全感問題<br />\n但依家諗返起都覺得自己好戇鳩 佢其實對我好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事後我有挽回 但佢話佢都諗清楚都係分手算<br />\n佢話有分手念頭就係已經破壞咗成段關係 唉</blockquote><br />\n情況一樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗返都覺得自己好戇鳩 講分手係我 後悔又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c3926d4b57c3918731fb10ded8e6780c472220","tid":174444,"uid":72342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T23:16:30.000Z","msg":"抵死  鬼叫你講分手   同人地老母岩岩死左 你就屌人老母一樣    唔同你真係分手就奇啦    你咩都收收埋埋 呢個可能就係問題所在 佢覺得你咩都唔講   自然就會淡   你要提分手  佢仲唔走？  一係你就chur番佢   唔係就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830dc5bb33179c1a3b395eca8193eaefeaade3c4","tid":174444,"uid":59804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T23:22:41.000Z","msg":"女人成日話做朋友<br />\n但男人覺得做朋友=有機<br />\n唔想呃自己/比你吊住"},{"pid":"cfc0fd70becc23447b846fb6dcf211f0ab89b248","tid":174444,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:00:13.000Z","msg":"點解你地女人唔明白，當你開口講分手既時候其實代表左好多野，而當佢花左好多時間接受既時候都代表左佢已經令自己死心。<br />\n你話人分左手之後絕情，點解唔諗吓自己講分手既時候絕唔絕情？<br />\n好多時候聽到呢兩隻字真係會心痛。<br />\n<br />\n利申：過來人<br />\n當我想選擇move on，真係唔會想返去以前既沼澤。好多時間感情就係俾呢啲嘢消耗殆盡。"},{"pid":"35d86238998f57a52e4cc4aa04621fd43ba8157f","tid":174444,"uid":69359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:05:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>連朋友都唔想做？<br />\n我仲好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因乜事分手先？</blockquote><br />\n我自己好衝動講咗分手 因為安全感問題<br />\n但依家諗返起都覺得自己好戇鳩 佢其實對我好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事後我有挽回 但佢話佢都諗清楚都係分手算<br />\n佢話有分手念頭就係已經破壞咗成段關係 唉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解可以咁易講得出呢d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你自己絕成咁怪唔到人 佢應該死左心"},{"pid":"0a012dfa71d7f703f618651f97d70e81f72dd255","tid":174444,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:08:43.000Z","msg":"男人,你肯哄多數哄到,純粹講心<br />\n絕係多數睇唔出你有心或者你一早已經破壞曬件事  <br />\n<br />\n女人好多時講完掛住,然後所有野都態度照舊,要哄講心講金講埋timing 都未必哄得返,要既野永遠有變數"},{"pid":"30a8908868b84cefe93086dd705d240eb26e5c26","tid":174444,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:10:06.000Z","msg":"分手完做朋友，未放低嗰一方會好撚痛苦<br />\n<br />\n如果大家互相冇晒感情，做朋友就冇咩問題嘅"},{"pid":"3410bcbfdc74bbeb0892b5344a7827ce6b49a8cd","tid":174444,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:13:45.000Z","msg":"女人先絕呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350493ad9a1f85f2